{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验探究，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解物体所受</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重力的大小跟质量的关系</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">静止时，弹簧测力计的示数等于钩码所受重力的大小。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计、钩码</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.观察弹簧测力计，确定它的量程和分度值。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.检查</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计的指针是否指在</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">零位上，如果不在，应该</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把指针</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调节</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">零位上</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.逐次增挂钩码，分别测出他们所受的重力，并记录在下面的表格中</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; font-family:Calibri; font-size:13px; width:582px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:115px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量m/kg</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:115px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重力G/N</span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:77px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.以质量为横坐标、重力为纵坐标描点并连接这些点。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总结物体所受重力跟它的质量的关系。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物体所受的重力跟它的质量成正比。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重力方向竖直向下。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地球附近的物体所受的重力与它的质量之间的关系为</span>g=G/m</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}